quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  18,17,"Hi…óa yi'a naangi ngen si nge ∆īellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe senngo √Īaamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay …ďe ka senngo nano, kam…ďe hi…ďe e yaajeende e …óun, …óun ko jeyaa…óun e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, kala moO majjini a he…ďantaa mo hettu…óo fewnoowo. @Corrected"
  18,18,"Hi…óa sikka …ďe ko …ďe finu…ďe, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe …óaanii…ďe, Me…óen waylitira …ďe senngo √Īaamo e senngo nano, rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun no fonti kay…óe mun …óen ka dammbugal, si a ∆īellitike e ma…ď…ďe a huccitayno e ma…ď…ďe dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri …ďe fii yo …ďe lanndondir hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e ma…ď…ďe: \"No foti hewde ko √Īii…ďu…óon?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Men √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa go…ó…óun e √Īallal.\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko √Īii…ďu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri laa…ďude √Īaamitee, yo o addan on √Īaametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ďe si …ďe ∆īellitike e mon …ďe rajmay on, maa…óun …ďe rutta on e laawol ma…ď…ďe ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii ma…ď…ďe, fii yo …ďe anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ďe poo…óondiraynoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fiyaake ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore ma…ď…ďe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe woni Anndu…óo fii Ma…ď…ďe.\" ∆Āen foolu…ďe e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow ma…ď…ďe Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray …ďe wi'a: \"Ko …ďe tato naya…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njowo njeega…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ko fampaangol ka ni…ďe.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ď…ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa see…óaa…ďe.\" Wata a wennju fii ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yewtere fee√Īunde, wata a lanndo fii ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi wa…óay …óun janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko …ďuri …ďadaade immorde e …óun Peewal"
  18,25,"∆Āe √Īii…ďi ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ďe …ďeydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko …ďe √Īii…ďi, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ďe gaanin Makko gi…óo, O kafidaa ka √Ďaawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ďataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maa…óa kin wonndude e …ďen noddoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe hi…ďe faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa …óe yawtu gaayi ma…ď…ďe hara hi…óa faandii cu…óaari ngurdan aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Men welsindini …ďernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gom…óin mono faalaa yo o yeddu, Menen Men heblanii too√Īoo…ďe …ďen Yiite no hunnditi …ďe …óen…óe magge …óen si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii faabo, …ďe faaboree ndiyan wa'u…óan wa sila taynaa…óo …óan ju…óa geece …óen, bonii njaram bonii werde"
  18,30,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala mo∆ī∆īin…óo golle"
  18,31,"∆Āen …óon no woodani …ďe Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal can…ói no ila ley ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe cu…óiree ton immorde e jawe kanŇče …ďe …ďornoo conci haaki…óu…ói …óewlu…ói e jalbu…ói ko …ďe so…ď…ďindii…ďe=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, mo∆ī∆īii mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īii kadi fowtorde"